      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十月十五日　昼",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、お誕生日おめでと～！　今日はこっそり\nみんなでお弁当を作ってきたの。じゃ～ん！",
      "startTime": 7.0333334287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　荷物多いなって思ってたけど\nそれお弁当箱だったの……！？　四段もある",
      "startTime": 14.2666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はりきって作り過ぎちゃった。さくらちゃんなんて\n朝からお仕事なのに、ギリギリまで手伝ってくれたの",
      "startTime": 22.9000000358,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15766.6666667,
          "startTime": 38.6666667025
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌の企画の方も手伝ってくれたのに、ありがたや……\nみんなの真心が染みる。……じゃあ早速、いただきます",
      "startTime": 32.0666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "むむ……このとんかつは間違いなくさくらちゃん\n怜ちゃんのに入れた時は解凍し忘れてたらしいけど……",
      "startTime": 44.5666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "今回のは自然解凍OKのだからか、バッチリ。こっちの\nタコさんウインナーは、たぶん琴乃ちゃんと渚ちゃん？",
      "startTime": 54.1666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "どっちも正解だよ～。あ、そのおにぎりは、遙子さんと\n怜ちゃんが作ってくれたの。具が、ぶり大根なんだ",
      "startTime": 63.8262205323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "『REI♡HARU』の特製おにぎり、エモい\nこっちの卵焼きは、千紗ちゃんと沙季ちゃんだったり？",
      "startTime": 72.4666677197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん。雫ちゃんの好きなおかずはもちろん\nそれぞれの、おすすめのものを入れてみたんだ～",
      "startTime": 80.1333333691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの好きが詰まってるんだね\nえ、じゃあ、どこかにくさやも……",
      "startTime": 87.0666636507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは止めておいたから大丈夫だよ\n「体にいいのに」ってしばらく言ってたけど……",
      "startTime": 95.7000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "あと、四段目はプリンとかドーナツでパンパンで……\n入り切らないから、グミはドーナツの穴に入れてて",
      "startTime": 104.3666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "欲張り過ぎたビュッフェみたいになってる……\nでも、ふふ。なんだか星見プロみたいに賑やか",
      "startTime": 112.1000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにみんなにお祝いしてもらえるなんて、嬉しい\nファンの人達も、SNSで一杯お祝いしてくれてるし",
      "startTime": 122.0333333691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。みんな、雫ちゃんのことが大好きだからね\n一緒にサニピになってくれて、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 132.1666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "出来ないことも多くて、落ち込んでばかりの私だけど\n雫ちゃんがいてくれたから、頑張ってこれたんだと思う",
      "startTime": 140.299996984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……。私の方こそありがとう。千紗ちゃんの\n頑張る姿を見て、自分も頑張ろうって何度も思ってきた",
      "startTime": 149.4666636507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……。えへへ、なんだかくすぐったいね\nあ、どうぞどうぞ、続き食べちゃって",
      "startTime": 161.099996984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "うん。一杯あるから、千紗ちゃんも一緒に食べよう？\n二人で食べたら、もっと美味しいと思うから",
      "startTime": 168.9333303173,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}